{"tid":2440122,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦問題求救","createTime":"2021-03-09T17:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T05:17:37.000Z","uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"43e8982b3c2f036aabefedb2b4995f7fb7112bc2","tid":2440122,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"2個月前去centralfeild 砌左部機<br />\n<br />\nTUF Gaming B550M Plus<br />\nAMD Ryzen 7 3700X 8-Core 3.59 Hz<br />\nGeforce RTX 2060<br />\n16GB ram x 2  冇左個名<br />\n牛都唔記得<br />\n1T SSD <br />\n<br />\n我返到屋企自己裝window 10<br />\n而家個問題係, 用用下電腦<br />\n就會hang<br />\nhang 既意思係, 隻滑鼠郁到, 但撳乜野冇反應<br />\n如果睇緊youtube 係繼續有聲, 但畫面停左<br />\n之後滑鼠click 任何野都變左圈圈 (loading)<br />\nctrl + alt + del 冇反應<br />\n我一定要reboot<br />\n通常呢個問題會喺我切換視窗時發生<br />\n例如睇緊youtube 開game 打<br />\n或打緊機開chrome 上youtube 聽歌<br />\n一開就會hang <br />\n<br />\n另外仲有就係<br />\n熄機時, 有80% 機會係mon熄左, 但風扇照轉, 機箱前面個燈仲著<br />\n我要熄就要長撳開機制3秒先熄到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果連登解決唔到<br />\n有邊個上門檢查可靠d？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb7cd5fbd1af9cd78fdea172c3ea6b8a8e19313","tid":2440122,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"講多少少<br />\n<br />\n我今日就上官網更新左bios<br />\n<br />\n之前google 過見到可能關個咩SATA Controller 事<br />\n我轉返做AMD 自己出嘅驅動，del 左microsoft 嗰個<br />\n<br />\n冇好轉過"},{"pid":"affcc65bec0b61d4f68f8c3300bbf99c7f4a3eff","tid":2440122,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:15:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6882e2dfb14ce5b9598cd77996ef88e0c30fe4bf","tid":2440122,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdbdf7db363dac51d7ea623c901cce0081a38c1","tid":2440122,"uid":374922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T